// Windows resource script — the sole purpose is the executable's file/shortcut
// icon. Resource ID 1 is the lowest-numbered ICON, which is the one Explorer, the
// taskbar and the Apps list use for `duja.exe`. The icon itself is the committed,
// generated whirlpool (see `examples/gen_exe_icon.rs`).
//
// Deliberately NO manifest here: the PerMonitorV2 DPI manifest is embedded
// separately by `embed-manifest` in build.rs, and two manifest resources would
// clash.
1 ICON "assets/duja.ico"
